 Galvatron laughed. "Optimus wont find me. With oiur link I have sent him a 
fake location of myself. He will be chaseing a phantom signature. But just in 
case." 
He sent a comm to Guildart and Megastrom.."Come to me now." He then sent a 
comm to Magma..."Optimujs and three other maxis may be on there way here. I 
am short a man and I wish to know if you would send me cerberus."
 He turned his attention back to enertron. "You shall die."
He shot two energy blast from both hands. The second they left his hand he 
flipped behind the bot before the energy even reached him. If he turned he 
would be hit by the blasts or he would be hit by the two rockets Galvatron 
released from his chest as he landed.

--part1_27.10e72cd5.27ac6808_boundary
